name: PS GoLive
overview: PS GoLive LLC provides services for PeopleSoft Enterprise products and business processes. It offers project charter development; detailed requirements analysis; software design and build; unit testing; integrated system testing; training; project management services to deploy and manage iPath controlled projects; implementation planning workshop; project quality audit; business process definition/customization design; development and delivery; test planning; technical administration; and upgrade planning services. The company offers services for PeopleSoft Enterprise products and business processes that focus on supply chain management, customer relationship management, and on integrated financials. It serves manufacturing, distribution, and or services industries. The company was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in North Palm Beach, Florida. As of November 25, 2008, PS GoLive LLC operates as a subsidiary of Zanett Inc.
